    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i'll check the drainage. you mentioned nitrogen though, is there a specific way to check if the soil is actually low on that? i'm also worried about the soil acidity/ph messing things up. how do i test that and how do i change it if it's off?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
